This sample  demonstrates  the WearableListView and lists the Sensors available on your Wear device. 

In order to run/test this app, install the Wear App to your Wear device.

How to build and install
-------------------------
Install Wear App
  Connect Wear  device via USB
  $ cd wear
  $ gradle clean installDebug

Running
  start the wList app. You should see a listview with a list of sensors available/detected for your device. 


Source code for book : Wearable Android - Android Wear and Google Fit / WILEY 2015
-- Sanjay M. Mishra
